                <h4 style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Bize Ulaşın</h4>
                <p><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt" style="color: #004284; margin-right: 10px;"></i> <strong>Adres:</strong> Merkez/Sivas</p>
                <p><i class="fas fa-phone" style="color: #004284; margin-right: 10px;"></i> <strong>Telefon:</strong> +(90) 212 111 22 33</p>
                <p><i class="fas fa-envelope" style="color: #004284; margin-right: 10px;"></i> <strong>E-posta:</strong> info@teknomarketim.com</p>
                <p><i class="fas fa-clock" style="color: #004284; margin-right: 10px;"></i> <strong>Çalışma Saatleri:</strong> Hafta içi 09:00 - 18:00</p>
            </div>
